                <h1>&#039;Adderall makes work fun&#039;</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/1c0c94d7-4be2-4246-9bad-b17512b4af6c.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="During&#x20;the&#x20;most&#x20;stressful&#x20;times&#x20;of&#x20;the&#x20;year,&#x20;more&#x20;and&#x20;more&#x20;Duke&#x20;students&#x20;are&#x20;turning&#x20;to&#x20;prescription&#x20;medications&#x20;like&#x20;Adderall&#x20;to&#x20;manage&#x20;the&#x20;stress&#x20;of&#x20;rigorous&#x20;academic." class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            During the most stressful times of the year, more and more Duke students are turning to prescription medications like Adderall to manage the stress of rigorous academic.

                                                             <aside class="photo-caption photo-credit d-block pl-1">
                                    <figcaption class="d-block">
                                                                                    Photo by <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/alexander-deckey">Alexander Deckey</a> |
